From: Janne Grunau <janne-libav@jannau.net>
Date: Tue, 3 Jun 2014 11:24:15 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 124/131] aarch64: remove optional :pg_hi21: for adrp
 instruction

Clang's integrated assembler does not support it.

Signed-off-by: Linus Yang <laokongzi@gmail.com>
---
 libavutil/aarch64/asm.S | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/libavutil/aarch64/asm.S b/libavutil/aarch64/asm.S
index fb635d0..b23eb4f 100644
--- a/libavutil/aarch64/asm.S
+++ b/libavutil/aarch64/asm.S
@@ -61,7 +61,7 @@ ELF     .size   \name, . - \name
         adrp            \rd, \val@PAGE
         add             \rd, \rd, \val@PAGEOFF
 #elif CONFIG_PIC
-        adrp            \rd, :pg_hi21:\val
+        adrp            \rd, \val
         add             \rd, \rd, :lo12:\val
 #else
         ldr             \rd, =\val
